ExtraDesc carriage stone orc~
This is a large slave propelled stone carriage. The 8 slaves are all 7 foot, 
300 pound, black hided orcs that march to the beat of the chant they are 
constantly mumbling. It is 11 foot tall, 10 feet long, and 6 feet wide in 
all and the door itself is atleast 9 feet in height and 5 and a half feet in 
width. It has two stone rear wheels that are one foot in width and four feet 
in diameter, and one wheel in the in the front which is 10 inches in width 
and 3 feet in diameter. The door has two fairly large paw prints engraved on 
it, the name "Mersen Murkat" engraved in an arch underneath the paw prints, 
and the door handle is a long and thick polished gold bar with intricate 
designs. The steps are made of black cast iron and have hundreds of ridges 
on them.The body of the carriage is blackened granite that was not not 
previously smoothed. 
~
